skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: chem equations
des:
Tell Alexa what compound you would like to know the formula of, and she will find it for you.
The list of compounds currently supported is the following:
Silicon Dioxide, Citric Acid, Glucose, Acetone, Sodium Hypochlorite, Calcium Oxide, Benzene, Nitrous Oxide, Calcium Hydroxide, Acetate, Phosphoric Acid, Methanol, Nitric Acid, Calcium Carbonate, Ethyl Group, Sodium Hydroxide, Ammonium, Sodium Carbonate, Bicarbonate, Hydrogen Peroxide, Hydrochloric Acid, Ethanol, Sodium Bicarbonate, Sugar, Acetic Acid, Sulfuric Acid, Methane, Carbon Dioxide, Sodium Chloride, Ammonia, Water.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
